00:45:55.800 --> 00:46:02.800
So things that are interesting about Veniver that I think is something that we should be excited about is it's very composable.

00:46:02.800 --> 00:46:10.800
So internally with Veniver API and Veniver model, Veniver APIs are just Plumber APIs.

00:46:10.800 --> 00:46:29.800
So if you're someone who is a Plumber expert and wants to add in new endpoints, wants to add in, you know, whatever other infrastructure you want around this Plumber endpoint, you can add that into your Veniver API just as you'd expect.

00:46:29.800 --> 00:46:33.800
It's also something that is built to be kind of an extension of a data science workflow.

00:46:33.800 --> 00:46:40.800
So you don't have to change the types of models you're creating or anything like that.

00:46:40.800 --> 00:46:48.800
It is truly just something to add on, not to try to change what you're already doing.

